ygData.messageBody:
In my experiences the dry bones out there in lake rathe which drop the
small bronze are QUITE difficult, and would con deep red at level 12, as
I believe the range up to 20, if not 22 or so. at level 29 there's
still dry bones out there that con blue to me, definetly not a thing to
be taken on unless you've great confidence in your abilities.
